PREDICT LIST_DISTINCT(TRANSACTIONS.ARTICLE_ID) OVER (30 DAYS FOLLOWING) RANK TOP 12 FOR EACH CUSTOMERS.CUSTOMER_ID
PREDICT target.multicategorical_column RANK TOP 20 FOR EACH target.id
